OL,3,CMan charged with arson following
OL,4,CDoncaster hotel fire
OL,6,FA man has been charged with arson with
OL,7,Fintent to endanger life following a
OL,8,Fhotel fire in Doncaster which saw
OL,9,Fguests evacuated and a hotel room
OL,10,Fdestroyed.
OL,12,FEmergency services were called to
OL,13,Freports of a fire at the Holiday Inn
OL,14,FExpress in Balby on Monday, 26 January.
OL,16,FSouth Yorkshire Police officers were
OL,17,Fdeployed to the scene and entered the
OL,18,Fhotel to assess the extent of the fire.
