OL,3,CMan charged with arson following
OL,4,CDoncaster hotel fire
OL,6,FAmid concerns for a person's safety in
OL,7,Fa room filled with smoke, officers
OL,8,Ftried to push the door open but were
OL,9,Fforced back by intense heat and flames.
OL,11,FWith the assistance of a hotel
OL,12,Femployee, officers used multiple fire
OL,13,Fextinguishers to try and douse the
OL,14,Fflames.
OL,16,FPC Warren Crowcroft then began
OL,17,Fclearing the hotel floor-by-floor,
OL,18,Fguiding guests and staff outside to
OL,19,Fsafety.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/5
