OL,3,CMan charged with arson following
OL,4,CDoncaster hotel fire
OL,6,FAfter ensuring the hotel was empty, he
OL,7,Fthen directed firefighters towards the
OL,8,Froom on fire resulting in the blaze
OL,9,Fbeing successfully extinguished.
OL,11,FAs this was all happening, PC Rowan
OL,12,FBurnett carried out enquiries to
OL,13,Flocate and apprehend the suspect.
OL,15,FDoncaster Response Sergeant Hannah Cox
OL,16,Fpraised the pair's actions along with
OL,17,Fthe member of hotel staff who
OL,18,Fsupported our officers during this
OL,19,Flive incident.
