OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F366A1769900048
OL,3,CMan charged with arson following
OL,4,CDoncaster hotel fire
OL,6,FShe said: "The actions of PC Crowcroft
OL,7,Fand PC Burnett epitomise what it means
OL,8,Fto be a response officer.
OL,10,F"Even when faced with danger, they
OL,11,Fdidn't hesitate entering the building
OL,12,Fand ensured their main priority was to
OL,13,Fprotect the public and keep them safe
OL,14,Ffrom harm.
OL,16,F"Given how quickly the fire took hold,
OL,17,Fthe outcome could have been very
OL,18,Fdifferent had it not been for their
OL,19,Fquick thinking and courage, and I am
OL,20,Fimmensely proud of their actions."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/5
