OL,3,CMan charged with arson following
OL,4,CDoncaster hotel fire
OL,6,FBradley Bennett, aged 32, of Ridgill
OL,7,FAvenue, Doncaster, has since been
OL,8,Fcharged with arson with intent to
OL,9,Fendanger life.
OL,11,FHe appeared before Barnsley
OL,12,FMagistrates' Court on Tuesday, 27
OL,13,FJanuary, and has been remanded in
OL,14,Fcustody ahead of his next hearing at
OL,15,FSheffield Crown Court on 24 February.
